# Environment Configuration for MaxDiagnostic

# Speed Test Configuration
# For private development: set to your local IP address (e.g., http://192.168.1.100:7000/librespeed_runner.html)
# For open source contributors: localhost will be used as fallback if this is not set
# SPEED_TEST_URL=http://localhost:7000/librespeed_runner.html

# Local Development Tips:
# - On Windows/Mac with Docker Desktop: use localhost
# - On Linux: may need host IP (check `ip route | grep default`)
# - For mobile testing: use your computer's IP address on the same network
# - Port 7000 is configured in docker/librespeed/docker-compose.yml
